The paper discusses the use of millimeter wave frequencies for accurate positioning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of a 3-D map for localization, which could fall under the sub-categories of Multimedia (cs.MM) and Robotics (cs.RO).
